Agnès Laurent https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Agn%C3%A8s_Laurent 0 Agnès Laurent (28 January 1936 – 16 February 2010) was a French actress. She mainly acted in France, but she could be mainly known to British people from playing the title role in the British comedy film A French Mistress.
